311
00:22:49,680 --> 00:22:51,140
Tunggu saja kabar di rumah.

312
00:22:51,270 --> 00:22:52,510
Setelah kasus tersebut diselesaikan,

313
00:22:52,510 --> 00:22:54,370
Pihak berwenang akan memberi tahu Anda.

314
00:22:54,640 --> 00:22:55,400
