[Penginapan Barat Laut]

399
00:26:29,830 --> 00:26:30,960
Hati-hati, Tuanku.

400
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:32,270
Perhatikan anak tangga.

401
00:26:38,240 --> 00:26:39,310
Jenderal, mohon tetap di sini.

402
00:26:39,310 --> 00:26:40,440
Tidak perlu mengantar saya.

403
00:26:40,590 --> 00:26:41,270
Jaga diri baik-baik, Tuanku.

404
00:26:41,270 --> 00:26:43,200
Maafkan saya karena tidak mengantar Anda keluar.

405
00:26:49,070 --> 00:26:51,210
