406
00:26:51,400 --> 00:26:53,660
Ekspresinya tetap datar sepanjang waktu.

407
00:26:54,300 --> 00:26:55,170
Mengapa demikian?

408
00:26:55,990 --> 00:26:58,430
Faksi Guru Besar Li
dan faksi Perdana Menteri Wei

409
00:26:58,430 --> 00:26:59,790
