410
00:26:59,790 --> 00:27:01,770
Setiap pejabat di pengadilan mengetahuinya.

411
00:27:01,770 --> 00:27:03,350
Namun jika menyangkut Tuan Li,

412
00:27:03,350 --> 00:27:05,610
