Marquis Wu'an?

413
00:27:03,410 --> 00:27:06,380
[Penginapan Barat Laut]

414
00:27:05,720 --> 00:27:06,690
Tepat.

415
00:27:07,960 --> 00:27:08,820
Coba pikirkan.

416
